race.comment: SINGING STAR (6) added to a long run of top three finishes with a closing third in a similar race to this 16 days ago. Drawn to enjoy a nice run behind a hot tempo and will be difficult to hold out. ETOILE FILANTE (2) is back from a nine-month spell and has transferred from the Hayes stable to Kris Lees. Showed plenty of talent when trained in Victoria and a good recent trial here suggests he is ready to make his mark. NO STATEMENT (1) led but found one better over this course and distance recently. Five-time winner here over 900m. Perfectly drawn and is always a threat. MR TRACKSIDE (8) returns from a 24-week lay-off. Trialling well and this is his optimum trip. Ready to make an immediate splash. PRINCESS CRUIZER (5) hasn't won for a while but is worth including in exotics.
